{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The remaining pieces show a clean path: a store-backed toast system can sit beside React Query and the connection hook without invasive rewrites. I\u2019m checking the chat pane now because the workspace already has event-stream state, and th...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_40", "text": "The remaining pieces show a clean path: a store-backed toast system can sit beside React Query and the connection hook without invasive rewrites. I\u2019m checking the chat pane now because the workspace already has event-stream state, and that\u2019s the right place to expose non-blocking connection banners instead of inventing a second status model.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 83, "prompt_index": 29, "prompt_name": "28 \u2014 Error, Loading, and Feedback States", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T03:34:06-07:00"}
